`await`. When `NavigationSystem.travel_completed` fires synchronously inside `initiate_travel()`, the coroutine suspends at `await _fade_out()` within the signal emission call stack. The tween's `finished` signal cannot properly resume the coroutine in this nested context, causing the transition to stall with inputs locked.\n\n## Test plan\n- [ ] Verify pressing CONFIRM TRAVEL triggers visible biome transition (fade out → scene load → fade in)\n- [ ] Verify player inputs are re-enabled after transition completes\n- [ ] Verify selected biome loads correctly\n- [ ] Verify all existing unit tests pass\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\nEOF\n)\" --base main","description":"Create PR targeting main"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":191,"cache_read_input_tokens":155816,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":191},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e95448fc-7558-4157-960a-6c7229146ac9","uuid":"a7f37954-fc60-498b-b8c1-8b56e41079ec"},{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0168uWfDgZ3XAWvpvp2bShGN","type":"tool_result","content":"https://github.com/sqlhammer/Hammer-Forge-Studio/pull/213","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e95448fc-7558-4157-960a-6c7229146ac9","uuid":"dd713b8c-0d89-4766-9dd4-81cf5f31a005","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"https://github.com/sqlhammer/Hammer-Forge-Studio/pull/213","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}},{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01YUcZST2HG3kEnQrNqX9dgV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01BxSEgA4gx1wXkaMAM3YuQP","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cd /c/repos/Hammer-Forge-Studio/.claude/worktrees/orch-gamepla